(41, 10, 22, 49, 5, 5, 5, 'great possessions', 'Connection of Wealth and Inheritance', 'Both passages emphasize the consequences of covetousness and attachment to possessions. The rich man''s sadness in Mark reflects the warning in Ephesians about the fate of the covetous regarding their inheritance.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini')
